`` Anaconda '' is a song by Trinidadian-born American rapper Nicki Minaj , from her third studio album , The Pinkprint -LRB- 2014 -RRB- .
It was released on August 4 , 2014 by Young Money Entertainment , Cash Money Records , and Republic Records as the second single from the album .
The song was produced by Polow da Don , Anonymous , and Da Internz .
The song heavily samples `` Baby Got Back '' by Sir Mix-a-Lot .
The song peaked at number two on the US Billboard Hot 100 , consequently becoming Minaj 's highest charting single in the United States to date .
It went on to spend eight weeks in the top ten of the Hot 100 chart .
The song also peaked within the top ten in Australia , Canada , Ireland , New Zealand and the United Kingdom .
An accompanying video for the song was directed by Colin Tilley and released on August 19 , 2014 .
Following the video 's release , it broke the 24-hour streaming record on Vevo by accumulating 19.6 million views in its first day of release , being surpassed by Taylor Swift 's `` Bad Blood '' in 2015 .
To further promote the song , Minaj performed it live at the 2014 MTV Video Music Awards and also performed it at Fashion Rocks and the iHeartRadio Music Festival .
`` Anaconda '' was nominated for Best Rap Song at the 2015 Grammy Awards .
The song was also nominated for two categories at the 2015 MTV Video Music Awards , Best Female Video and Best Hip-Hop Video , winning the latter .